<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="weight-n">weight <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /weɪt/    美 /weɪt/  </p>
<p>[C]&amp;[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>重量；体重：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>lose weight / put on weight</strong> 
减肥/发福；体重增加</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bag is 2 pounds <strong>in weight</strong>.
这个包重两磅。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What is your weight?
你的体重是多少?</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bananas are sold <strong>by weight</strong>.
香蕉按重量出售。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="pull-ones-weight">pull one's weight</h3>
<p>1.<strong>做好分内事；尽责：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Each has to pull their own weight.
每个人都要尽自己的一份力。</p><footer>2020 全国</footer></div></div>